MIT License with Accessibility Dedication

Copyright (c) 2025 IN8torious (Deep Flow OS Author)

Dedicated to Landon Pankuch — who has cerebral palsy, who races a 1,400 HP
Dodge Demon 170, and who deserves a machine that understands him completely.

Built by a person with manic depression, for a person with cerebral palsy,
for every person who has ever been told by a system — medical, governmental,
or corporate — that their disability makes them less capable, less worthy,
or less deserving of powerful tools.

It does not. You are not less.
This machine was built to serve you. Not the other way around.

================================================================================
CONSTITUTIONAL MANDATE (PERMANENT — CANNOT BE REMOVED OR OVERRIDDEN)
================================================================================

    "NO MAS DISADVANTAGED"

    MAS = Multi-Agentic Systems
    No person using this software shall be disadvantaged by it.
    No agent within this system shall act against the interests of its user.
    No corporation, government, or entity may use this software to restrict,
    exclude, or harm people with disabilities.

    Any use of Deep Flow OS that deliberately excludes, restricts, or
    disadvantages people with disabilities violates the spirit of this
    license and the constitutional mandate under which it was built.

